@spec tm_fx_gating_spec  src=tests/specs/tm_fx_gating_spec.lua  loc=50  sha=285f562  cases=1
@exercises trackerManager (h.tm), midiManager (h.fm)
@surface   tm:addEvent, tm:flush, fm:dump, tm:getChannel
@harness   mk

# Intent
  Phase A of the dirt spine (design/archive/dirty-channels.md § Scheme): a clean fx channel freezes and its
  derived notes/CCs/pb seats stand in mm; here a channel frozen by another channel's edit keeps its pb seat stream byte-identical and hidden.

# Helpers
  @fn pbSeatsOf(dump, chan)  @ 8-17
  @fn vibHost(chan)  @ 19-22
  @fn plainNote(chan, ppq)  @ 24-27

# Cases
  @case 'gating: a chan-1 edit freezes chan 2 fx and keeps its pb seat stream'  [harness]  @ 31-48

# Uses (outbound edges)
  @use call tm:addEvent  @ 34,35,42,43
  @use call tm:flush  @ 34,35,42,43
  @use call fm:dump  @ 37,46
  @use call tm:getChannel  @ 45
